WEBVTT

00:02.445 --> 00:06.417
Being a dad is more than being a father.

00:08.919 --> 00:09.829
It's a choice.

00:12.846 --> 00:15.965
A choice to get hurt, rather than to hurt.

00:20.097 --> 00:23.265
To be bold when others are scared.

00:26.321 --> 00:28.996
A choice that says you'll be there,...

00:30.979 --> 00:37.869
...to show them right from wrong by your words and by your actions.

00:38.905 --> 00:41.799
Being a dad is more than being a father.

00:43.002 --> 00:44.005
It's a commitment,...

00:44.727 --> 00:47.562
...one that will make a wonderful human being...

00:51.448 --> 00:54.227
...who will make their own choices someday.

